node.text:
@derrickgracetwo is clearly in love with his kids and wants them to have the best life possible. His perspective is, if I take care of my children, they may follow the example and step up like their father. Good point.

On the other side, is it possible to spoil the child? 🤔

I think the first thing we need to do is create a life that gives us this option lol 

Check out the @socialproofpodcast episode #166 featuring @derrickgracetwo this brother dropped a lot of game on me!
